author: @TheSaDeMa
text:
For everyone with questions about the choreography:
This choreography is a version of the choreography that was used in Xiuweet Time that was performed before Xiumin left for military service.
In turn, that choreography has some elements used in Magical Circus.
So, in conclusion, it is a mix of Shake's two previous choreographies, with some new elements.
I invite you all to see the two previous choreographies and compare it with this one to find the similarities and differences.
